# Lumen — environment variables
#
# Lumen is BRING-YOUR-OWN-KEY. API keys are NOT read from the environment.
# Each user enters their own keys in the in-app Settings tab; the keys live in
# the browser (localStorage) and are sent per-request as headers:
#   - Vercel AI Gateway key  -> Chat (Claude / Gemini / GPT, all via the gateway)
#   - Fal.ai key             -> Image / Video / Audio generation
#
# So there is nothing required here to deploy. The only optional flag:

# Force mock mode everywhere (ignore user keys) — handy for a pure offline demo.
# LUMEN_FORCE_MOCK=1
